{"tid":210378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裸男中環碼頭暢泳　春光乍現嚇親OL","createTime":"2017-04-21T01:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T04:44:17.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a45f0d6e99d70f8672f2bf144d60df559867513e","tid":210378,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:12:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>裸男中環碼頭暢泳　春光乍現嚇親OL</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170421/photo/bkn-20170421072450596-0421_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170421082705\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170421%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170421072450596-0421_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170421082705&h=e9abdbf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中環碼頭海面「春光乍現」，清晨6時許，一名全身赤裸男子在9號碼頭對開海面游泳，大批途人及搭船來往中環的上班族見狀為之側目。警員及消防員接報到場時，男子已游至離岸邊約200米遠位置。<br />\n<br />\n消防小艇駛近男子，惟男子拒絕登艇，且繼續愈游愈遠，消防只好派出2名蛙人落海參與救援，卒在1個多小時後，男子開始氣力不繼，遂由蛙人帶上小艇，再送返岸邊交由救護車送院。<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>惟男子並不領情，不停大叫：「咩事呀？依家游水犯法呀！</strong></span>」他情緒激動不斷掙扎，由於他一絲不掛，救護員用紅氈為他遮蔽身體，再將他綁在擔架床上，送院檢驗，女途人目睹不禁嘩然。由於事主答非所問，警方不排除事主精神失常引發一場鬧劇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b6f619b792e281be8fa34e30f2421a2af58308","tid":210378,"uid":41643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:13:09.000Z","msg":"傻人發現案"},{"pid":"57a2b6ff538a6aabe90b8b73471c1737e282f8a5","tid":210378,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:14:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce2f36405dfdb05e30bc59cecce1c665ffb55e3c","tid":210378,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:15:21.000Z","msg":"香港真係勁多痴線佬"},{"pid":"c7063984c26f64da1ba57950b865149e7e51036b","tid":210378,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:17:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=